
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">


<head>
   <meta charset="UTF-8">
   <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
   <title>Results</title>


   <!-- Boostrap Links -->
   <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
       integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
   <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
       integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
       crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
            color: #ffffff;
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        header>h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        header>h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 300;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .cont {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 20px 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: left;
            color: white;
        }

        .cont>p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: white;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

        ul>li {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin: 10px 0;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        ul>li::before {
            color: #ffdf00;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #ffdf00;
            color: #000;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background: #ffcc00;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .button:active {
            background: #e6b800;
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            color: white;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .carousel {
            padding: 25px;
        }

        /* Main Nav */


        nav, 
        .nav-link {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: row;
                color: rgb(250, 251, 251);
                text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
                
        }

        nav{
                justify-content: space-around;
                align-items: center;
                height: 12vh;
        }

        .nav-link {
                list-style: none;
                gap: 1rem;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        nav ul {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: row;
                /* padding: 0;
                margin: 0; */
                list-style: none;
                
                ;
        }

        nav ul li {
            /* margin: 0; */
                list-style: none; 
                
        }

        li a {
            display: block;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            /* padding: 14px 16px; */
            text-decoration: none;
        
        }

        a{
                color: black;
                text-decoration: none;
                text-decoration-color: white;
        }

        a:hover{
                color: yellow;
                text-decoration: underline;
                text-underline-offset: 1rem;
                text-decoration-color: yellow;
                
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Brush Script MT', cursive;
                font-size: 1.7rem;
                margin-right: 380px;
                color: yellow;
        }

        .logo:hover{
            cursor: default;
        } 
    </style>
</head>


<body class="darkmode">

     <!-- desktop-nav -->
 <nav id = "desktop-nav">
    <div class="logo"> ThinkStorm </div>
    <div>
    <ul class = "nav-links">
        <li><a href="/home">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/game">Game</a></li>
        <li><a href="/profile">Profile</a></li>
        
     </ul>
    </div>
</nav> 
  


   <div>
       <header>
           <h1>Results Of Your Quiz!</h1>
       </header>
   </div>


   <div class="cont">
        <strong>Name: </strong><span><%= currentuser %></span>
        <br>
        <strong>Score: </strong><span><%= score %></span> out of 100</span>
        <br>
        <strong>Feedback: </strong><span><%= feedback %></span>
        <br>
   </div>


   <div>
       <a href="/game"><button class="button">Play Again</button></a>
   </div>


   <footer>
       <p>&copy; 2025 ThinkStorm. All rights reserved. Your trivia adventure starts here!</p>
   </footer>


